_Controller
protected static enum _Controller.Type
extends java.lang.Enum<_Controller.Type>

Controller algorithm. The three-letter prefix indicates the broad class of the controller.

  • IRM, isolated ramp metering
  • CRM, coordinated ramp metering
  • VSL, variable speed limits
  • SIG, signal control (intersections)
